    "description": "Ebara Jitsugyo Co.,Ltd. manufactures and sells environmentally related products. The company operates through Manufacturing, Engineering, and Trading business segments. The company offers manufacturing businesses, such as ozone concentration meters, ozone application equipment, industrial deodorizers and deodorizing equipment, energy-saving blowers, water treatment related equipment, infectious disease prevention products, aquaculture related products, and ZEB/ZEH related products. It also offers engineering businesses, such as water and sewage treatment facilities, including water purification plants, sewage treatment plants, various pumping stations; related design, construction, and maintenance of machinery and electrical equipment; and cloud-based remote monitoring and control system E-Qias Cloud, water supply facilities, sewerage facilities, storm water drainage pumping station facility, manhole pump facility. In addition, the company is involved in trading business, such as pumps, blowers, air conditioning, building piping restoration work, energy, water supply degassing and ionization devices, steel structure, crusher, and spirion; and purchases and sells air conditioning equipment, cooling and heating equipment, etc. related to air conditioning equipment, water supply and drainage, sanitary equipment, etc., and construction related to the equipment. Further, it provides waste liquid/waste recycling equipment, waste sorting equipment, and waste treatment equipment; medical devices, chemicals, and reagents; contracts and executes civil engineering, building construction, electrical work, plumbing, steel structures, painting, machinery and equipment installation, and other construction work; real estate leasing and management activities; animal feed and organic fertilizers; leasing and rental business; industrial waste disposal business; and temporary staffing business. Ebara Jitsugyo Co.,Ltd. was incorporated in 1946 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
